      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires significant mechanical attention, as the engine runs roughly and there are noticeable leaks underneath. The exterior has substantial body damage, including heavy rusting on the rocker panels and several large dents. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears and stains, and several electronic features, including the AC, are non-functional. This would be an ideal project car or a source for parts for someone with the right tools and expertise.",
