    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. The exterior features several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives fine, but it lacks the smoothness of a newer model and may require some minor maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, high-mileage vehicle that is priced to reflect its current state.",
