      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s totally flawless and ready for a new home. I'm so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it. Drop me a message if you're interested\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43900.0,
