    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen boasts a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double-VANOS system. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with a reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox that provides precise, positive engagement. Power is managed via a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains factory-spec with intact bushings and original dampers, delivering the legendary MacPherson strut and multi-link rear suspension geometry without compromise. Finished in an immaculate Carbon Black, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a high-revving masterpiece in its purest, unmolested form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
